1
00:00:00,120 --> 00:00:01,599
Don't let the fire go out tonight.

2
00:00:01,600 --> 00:00:02,799
Bears come around here often.

3
00:00:03,560 --> 00:00:04,599
Thanks, Brother Wu.

4
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:12,239
You go into the mountains a lot.

5
00:00:12,240 --> 00:00:13,760
Have you ever been attacked by a bear?

6
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:14,919
Bears aren't as tall as me.

7
00:00:14,919 --> 00:00:15,919
They can't hurt me.

8
00:00:18,559 --> 00:00:20,280
Do I really look like a bear?

9
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:31,480
I never used to think about
how I'd survive without a signal.

10
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:33,600
And now?

11
00:00:35,679 --> 00:00:36,919
Being cut off from the world...

12
00:00:37,159 --> 00:00:38,520
is absolutely amazing.

13
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:41,920
You don't find it boring?

14
00:00:45,079 --> 00:00:46,999
It's like going back to
the Stone Age overnight.

15
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:15,000
"A Winter Sun Wakes the Wind in Spring Hills' Dream"

16
00:01:18,700 --> 00:01:20,700
(Episode 5: The Wilderness)

17
00:01:26,319 --> 00:01:28,319
Is that rumor about the rich woman true?

18
00:01:29,959 --> 00:01:31,599
You actually believe rumors like that?

19
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:38,079
With your current standing, how
could you land a variety show?

20
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:47,280
Can't I get one on my own merit?

21
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:51,079
Does no one have any faith in me?

22
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:55,199
Everyone says Qinglang
won Best Actor on merit.

23
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,560
Why does no one believe in me?

24
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:58,319
No one at all?

25
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,520
I'm sorry.

26
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:16,000
Sister Lan found out what I did for you.

27
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:19,319
Oh. Did she give you a hard time?

28
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,159
No. Just wait for me to get back.

29
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,400
Okay.

30
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:29,120
Love you, baby.

31
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,120
I'll be waiting for you.

32
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:41,439
What's this?

33
00:03:42,639 --> 00:03:44,039
Tea seed powder. It's eco-friendly.

34
00:03:51,439 --> 00:03:52,959
You really care about the environment.

35
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,160
But have you ever thought about this?

36
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,360
Once we reach the village...

37
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:58,360
where people actually live...

38
00:03:59,319 --> 00:04:02,639
and everyone goes back to
using detergent and shampoo...

39
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:06,160
the pollution will still wash
down the river to this very spot.

40
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:09,079
Just because I can't control the future...

41
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:11,320
doesn't mean I should
stop doing the right thing now.

42
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:13,360
At least I'm doing my part right now.

43
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:14,719
I won't have any regrets.

44
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,680
I can't believe he ran away with someone.

45
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,255
He's still not answering his phone.

46
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,040
It's probably just a bad signal.

47
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,040
I'm sure he's fine.

48
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,480
Are you warm enough?

49
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,560
Here's your strawberry.

50
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:34,360
Thank you.

51
00:04:34,361 --> 00:04:35,720
Wenshu replied.

52
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,638
She can talk now.

53
00:04:37,639 --> 00:04:38,639
Sister Lan.

54
00:04:40,959 --> 00:04:41,959
Hello, President Xu.

55
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:42,879
You're too polite, Sister Lan.

56
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:44,120
Just call me Wenshu.

57
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,360
I don't eat sweets when I'm filming.

58
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,120
Oh, please.

59
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,136
I've been eating double
portions for every meal.

60
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:52,120
I've put on so much weight
these past two months.

61
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,279
I heard that Tony is coming.

62
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,480
When will he be here?

63
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:57,879
He'll be here shortly.

64
00:04:58,519 --> 00:04:59,879
Watch your attitude.

65
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,480
I'll try.

66
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:03,920
Do you think I'm breaking out?

67
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:05,639
Let me see.

68
00:05:08,639 --> 00:05:09,639
Sister Lan.

69
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,480
Kevin.

70
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,480
Sister Jialin.

71
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:16,480
You must be exhausted
after the flight and the drive.

72
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,758
I just got off the bus.

73
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:20,079
I wanted to make sure I came
to see Sister Lan right away.

74
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,639
Sister Lan is on a call right now.

75
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:25,040
Cavin, you might need to wait a moment.

76
00:05:25,279 --> 00:05:26,279
Kevin.

77
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,878
Sister Lan is dealing with
an urgent matter right now.

78
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:30,696
Once she's done, I'll
bring her over to see you.

79
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,480
Oh, that won't do.

80
00:05:31,481 --> 00:05:33,096
You've already taken such
good care of my boy here.

81
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:35,480
Brother Guo, please show Kevin to his room.

82
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,040
Sure.

83
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,360
Are you afraid of Kevin?

84
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,120
It's not really fear.

85
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:55,279
I'm under contract, so I
have to do what I'm told.

86
00:05:55,959 --> 00:05:57,480
Our company isn't like that.

87
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,720
I know.

88
00:06:00,759 --> 00:06:03,920
I'd heard that Sister Lan was
different from other producers.

89
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,760
But I didn't quite believe it back then.

90
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,439
I actually really envy you.

91
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:10,839
Having someone like Sister Lan.

92
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:14,039
If I could work under
Sister Lan for a few years...

93
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,800
I'd definitely make
it big in the future.

94
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:19,240
The other day, I saw her taking out
the trash and moving tables herself.

95
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:21,479
It's like she can do absolutely
everything on her own.

96
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,720
"Never pin your hopes on others."

97
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,879
Yes, Sister Lan told me that.

98
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:34,639
It's our company slogan.

99
00:06:35,126 --> 00:06:36,526
It's hanging on the wall.

100
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,639
When I first joined...

101
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:40,479
and Sister Lan interviewed me...

102
00:06:40,959 --> 00:06:42,439
she said something to me...

103
00:06:42,879 --> 00:06:44,879
that I'll never forget
for the rest of my life.

104
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:46,879
I asked her...

105
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,319
if actors aren't allowed to date.

106
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,040
What did she say?

107
00:06:56,279 --> 00:06:57,480
She told me...

108
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,360
"You can date."

109
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,680
"But as an artist..."

110
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:03,879
"if you rely on your
fans for a living..."

111
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,640
"you must have basic
professional integrity."

112
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:09,480
"You can't take their money..."

113
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,400
"while deceiving them at the same time."

114
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,759
"That's cause and effect."

115
00:07:15,079 --> 00:07:16,479
"Everyone must bear the consequences..."

116
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,360
"of their own choices and actions."

117
00:07:20,959 --> 00:07:22,439
"But as your elder..."

118
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,680
"I support you dating."

119
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:27,680
"You have the right to experience life..."

120
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:30,639
"instead of being bound by a label."

121
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,319
At that moment, I realized...

122
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:37,119
I'd probably never find...

123
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,959
a boss more
understanding than Sister Lan.

124
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,639
So, I signed the contract.

125
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:47,519
Besides, all of Sister Lan's
works reflect who she is.

126
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:51,040
I believe that artistic expression...

127
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,959
is a reflection of the creator's soul.

128
00:07:54,639 --> 00:07:55,680
That's beautiful.

129
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:03,279
Yeah.

130
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,639
Let me ask you something.

131
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:08,879
Were Lang Di and Shi Yuhao together before?

132
00:08:10,079 --> 00:08:11,279
How should I know?

133
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,279
Aren't you psychic?

134
00:08:13,519 --> 00:08:14,799
Close your eyes and take a look.

135
00:08:40,279 --> 00:08:42,440
Old Man Chang wasn't surprised.

136
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:44,080
He asked Old Man Qing,

137
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:46,559
"Where are they?"

138
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:49,679
"They went back to the sea."

139
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:54,440
Old Man Qing looked longingly
at the sunset glow and said,

140
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:57,840
"They're all out at sea."

141
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:02,918
"They represent every
loved one and friend..."

142
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:05,320
"who had ever crossed
paths with the two old men."

143
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:09,480
Old Man Chang held Old
Man Qing's hands in one of his,

144
00:09:09,559 --> 00:09:12,039
and gently touched his face, saying,

145
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:15,960
"Yanyan, let's go back too."

146
00:09:17,159 --> 00:09:20,278
Snuggled together under
the bright, warm sun,

147
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:22,039
they returned to the sea together.

148
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:26,759
That year, Old Man Chang was 116 years old,

149
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:29,120
and his lover was 129.

150
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,840
He had fulfilled his childhood wish.

151
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:34,759
From the moment he met his love at 16,

152
00:09:34,879 --> 00:09:37,840
to 26, 36...

153
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:40,440
and finally to 116.

154
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:44,479
Spending a hundred years in this world...

155
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:46,855
sharing a hundred springs, summers,
autumns, and winters with his love.

156
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:49,679
That's a legendary kind
of happiness, isn't it?

157
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:55,159
By that logic,

158
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,279
I'll have to live to 118.

159
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,280
What are the main characters' names?

160
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:04,360
Old Man Chang and Old Man Qing.

161
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:05,840
I mean their real names.

162
00:10:07,559 --> 00:10:08,879
Changyang and Qinglang.

163
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:11,279
You're lying.

164
00:10:11,879 --> 00:10:13,559
Look for yourself if you don't believe me.

165
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:40,599
How long have we been out this time?

166
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,480
Who cares?

167
00:10:42,481 --> 00:10:44,321
I don't have any work
until next month anyway.

168
00:10:46,039 --> 00:10:47,039
Oh.

169
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,840
What are you drawing?

170
00:11:08,279 --> 00:11:10,120
Counting down the days until next month.

171
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,800
Including today, we have ten days left.

172
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,919
This scar on your head...

173
00:11:30,679 --> 00:11:31,879
From a fight when I was a kid.

174
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,360
You don't seem like the
type to get into fights.

175
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,159
You won't even argue with me.

176
00:11:39,879 --> 00:11:41,480
Don't you need me to go easy on you?

177
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,559
If you didn't truly understand me...

178
00:11:53,639 --> 00:11:54,840
you wouldn't be able to.

179
00:11:58,159 --> 00:11:59,360
You have a fiery temper.

180
00:12:00,629 --> 00:12:01,989
Before I used to
be worse than you.

181
00:12:05,480 --> 00:12:07,255
It's like you have
firecrackers in your pocket...

182
00:12:07,279 --> 00:12:09,479
ready to pull them out
and light them at any moment.

183
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,879
So why did you get into a fight?

184
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:15,759
Was someone bullying you?

185
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,679
I was backstabbed by my best friend.

186
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:21,520
They spread the rumor that
I was an illegitimate child.

187
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,720
I took on eight of them by myself.

188
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:31,079
I beat them so badly they
all ended up in the hospital.

189
00:12:33,665 --> 00:12:35,265
Is that why you came to Molie?

190
00:12:36,519 --> 00:12:37,519
Yeah.

191
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:42,559
But I realized the mountains
are cleaner than people's hearts.

192
00:12:43,279 --> 00:12:44,679
So I decided to stay.

193
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:10,039
Jin Jin.

194
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,720
I've always treated you
like family, haven't I?

195
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:17,759
Sister Jialin, you don't
have to say it. I resign.

196
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:20,735
I was the one who told Shi Yuhao
about Lang Di's whereabouts.

197
00:13:20,759 --> 00:13:22,479
Being a fangirl for a washed-up actor...

198
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:24,320
has more of a future
than working with me?

199
00:13:24,679 --> 00:13:25,919
I don't care about my future.

200
00:13:26,039 --> 00:13:27,039
I love Shi Yuhao.

201
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,840
I'd do anything for him.

202
00:13:29,159 --> 00:13:30,320
He's a total scumbag!

203
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:37,240
Jialin, did you settle Jin Jin's pay?

204
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,639
This girl is so stubborn.

205
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:41,559
I want her to see clearly that

206
00:13:41,639 --> 00:13:43,480
Shi Yuhao isn't worth
her sacrificing so much.

207
00:13:44,039 --> 00:13:45,039
Jin Jin.

208
00:13:45,679 --> 00:13:47,840
I hope you remember
the choice you made today.

209
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,840
No matter what happens in the future,

210
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:52,038
you must accept who you were today.

211
00:13:52,039 --> 00:13:53,080
That's enough.

212
00:13:53,759 --> 00:13:56,279
You only lost a job with me.

213
00:13:56,919 --> 00:13:59,239
I don't want you to lose

214
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:01,480
the impulse and passion of your youth.

215
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:06,679
Jialin, have the accountant
pay her in cash later.

216
00:14:08,552 --> 00:14:10,632
Sister Lan, I don't regret it.

217
00:14:11,159 --> 00:14:12,159
Good.

218
00:14:15,279 --> 00:14:16,840
Wow, happy wrap-up!

219
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,080
Happy wrap-up!

220
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:19,080
Happy wrap-up!

221
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,240
Great.

222
00:14:21,279 --> 00:14:22,240
Thank you, Sister Lan.

223
00:14:22,279 --> 00:14:23,439
Thank you for your hard work.

224
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,480
Go on.

225
00:15:37,639 --> 00:15:38,480
Oh, look at my hands.

226
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:39,480
Look at my hands.

227
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,840
What do you want to do in the future?

228
00:15:43,159 --> 00:15:45,720
You don't want to do just one
thing your whole life, do you?

229
00:15:47,679 --> 00:15:49,039
Sticking to one person is fine.

230
00:15:49,519 --> 00:15:50,759
Can you speak properly?

231
00:15:53,039 --> 00:15:54,359
If you hadn't come to Molie,

232
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:55,840
I was planning to leave.

233
00:15:56,679 --> 00:15:57,679
To where?

234
00:15:59,279 --> 00:16:00,840
I want to see other forests.

235
00:16:01,120 --> 00:16:03,360
I want to visit every forest in the world.

236
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,720
That's a great dream.

237
00:16:06,919 --> 00:16:07,919
You support it?

238
00:16:09,279 --> 00:16:10,279
Of course I do.

239
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,840
Don't you think it's crazy?

240
00:16:14,793 --> 00:16:16,153
If I quit showbiz,

241
00:16:16,279 --> 00:16:17,519
I'd be even crazier than you.

242
00:16:35,919 --> 00:16:36,999
It's not working very well.

243
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:40,120
Let's charge it when we
get back to the guesthouse.

244
00:16:41,559 --> 00:16:42,840
Being a caveman isn't easy.

245
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:46,400
I'm definitely going to get
scolded when I get back.

246
00:16:46,559 --> 00:16:47,879
I promised Sister Lan a cameo.

247
00:16:48,679 --> 00:16:50,959
Counting the days, they should
wrap up today or tomorrow.

248
00:16:51,039 --> 00:16:52,320
I probably won't make it.

249
00:16:54,039 --> 00:16:55,279
Sister Lan's new drama?

250
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:58,120
A remake of my movie from seven years ago.

251
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:03,039
I often hear people say

252
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:05,278
an actor's destiny will closely align

253
00:17:05,279 --> 00:17:06,919
with the character that made them famous.

254
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,759
Is that true for you too?

255
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:11,920
Not really.

256
00:17:13,039 --> 00:17:14,279
If it were that accurate,

257
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:17,680
I should have played a character
who wins Best Actor right away.

258
00:17:19,319 --> 00:17:20,919
It would have saved me a lot of detours.

259
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:26,519
Shi Yuhao is quite like his character.

260
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:29,279
Cowardly and indecisive.

261
00:17:32,720 --> 00:17:34,279
In that case, I'm quite like mine too.

262
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:36,960
I am brave,

263
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:40,640
steadfast in the path I choose,

264
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,720
and unwavering.

265
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:46,880
You too, right?

266
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,160
Tiantian.

267
00:18:07,359 --> 00:18:08,919
Now that Grandma is here,

268
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:10,559
neither you or Langlang are home.

269
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:12,439
If you two don't come back soon,

270
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:13,839
Grandma is going to throw a fit.

271
00:18:13,972 --> 00:18:15,891
Grandma, please stay a few more days.

272
00:18:15,915 --> 00:18:16,915
I'll fly back.

273
00:18:17,520 --> 00:18:20,158
Grandma, did my brother call home?

274
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:20,839
Huh?

275
00:18:20,840 --> 00:18:23,279
Did my brother, Feng Qinglang, call home?

276
00:18:23,319 --> 00:18:26,079
No. Is something wrong with your brother?

277
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,519
Your eldest grandson is missing.

278
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:28,815
He's hiding, and we can't find him.

279
00:18:28,839 --> 00:18:31,079
- Really?
- Who's calling?

280
00:18:32,279 --> 00:18:33,839
- My grandson.
- Don't tell Mom.

281
00:18:34,079 --> 00:18:35,160
I have to go, Grandma.

282
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:36,880
Okay, okay.

283
00:18:38,079 --> 00:18:39,440
Did he say what it was about?

284
00:18:41,039 --> 00:18:44,279
Yes, he said he missed his grandma.

285
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,440
Hello, Brother Wenshu.

286
00:19:07,839 --> 00:19:09,039
Did you find your brother?

287
00:19:09,319 --> 00:19:12,680
Not yet. I shouldn't have
treated him like an adult.

288
00:19:13,480 --> 00:19:14,560
You're not that old either.

289
00:19:15,079 --> 00:19:18,440
Brother Wenshu, I have
a confession to make.

290
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:19,880
What is it?

291
00:19:21,559 --> 00:19:22,440
Half a month ago,

292
00:19:22,441 --> 00:19:25,159
I talked to Changyang about going into
the mountains for the spring tea season.

293
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:27,079
Later, I brought my brother along.

294
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:30,079
Thinking back on it now,

295
00:19:30,759 --> 00:19:33,838
Changyang was the one who said the
mountains are peaceful and rejuvenating,

296
00:19:33,839 --> 00:19:35,119
perfect for a relaxing vacation.

297
00:19:36,119 --> 00:19:38,559
He also said he planned
to start a tea estate

298
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:41,079
to cater to out-of-town clients.

299
00:19:41,480 --> 00:19:42,960
And most importantly,

300
00:19:43,279 --> 00:19:44,679
he said, "I have a friend
who wants to come,

301
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:45,680
and I can host him."

302
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:47,960
Only now do I realize

303
00:19:48,839 --> 00:19:50,880
he was baiting me into
bringing my brother here.

304
00:19:51,359 --> 00:19:53,278
Back then, my brother had just announced

305
00:19:53,279 --> 00:19:55,136
his participation in the
variety show with Shi Yuhao.

306
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,518
The two fanbases were
at each other's throats,

307
00:19:56,519 --> 00:19:58,119
and my brother was extremely stressed.

308
00:19:58,680 --> 00:20:00,720
So you suspect Changyang
planned this all along?

309
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:04,439
If nothing was going on between them,

310
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:05,440
I wouldn't suspect him.

311
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:08,440
But now that he's run off with my brother,

312
00:20:09,119 --> 00:20:12,920
I feel really bad about
this, especially to you.

313
00:20:13,119 --> 00:20:14,399
You don't have to feel that way.

314
00:20:14,559 --> 00:20:17,559
Yes, I do. You've chased
my brother for three years.

315
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,758
If you hadn't invested in his movie,

316
00:20:19,759 --> 00:20:21,039
he wouldn't have won Best Actor.

317
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:22,880
Professionally and personally,

318
00:20:23,279 --> 00:20:24,519
I feel like we owe you.

319
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:26,520
Then think about how
you can make it up to me.

320
00:20:28,240 --> 00:20:29,440
I've already thought of a way.

321
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:31,239
I'll ask Changyang for his best tea,

322
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:32,160
and sell it to you at the lowest price.

323
00:20:32,161 --> 00:20:33,279
I'll help you make money.

324
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:36,480
Taking Changyang's money
and putting it in my pocket?

325
00:20:36,697 --> 00:20:38,295
Moving money from hand to hand?

326
00:20:38,319 --> 00:20:39,319
Exactly.

327
00:20:40,279 --> 00:20:42,279
Then I'll help you win my brother back.

328
00:20:42,839 --> 00:20:44,519
I'm afraid I don't have what it takes.

329
00:20:45,079 --> 00:20:46,479
Changyang is too clever.

330
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:47,759
And you're far away abroad.

331
00:20:47,839 --> 00:20:49,439
During my brother's days in Molie,

332
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:51,078
he pampered him down to his very hair.

333
00:20:51,079 --> 00:20:52,999
He's more devoted than anything.

334
00:20:53,559 --> 00:20:55,920
Don't overthink it. I don't blame you.

335
00:20:58,440 --> 00:21:00,640
How many other people do you call "baby"?

336
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:04,560
I can't believe I invested 50 million
to get you variety show resources,

337
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:06,359
and this is how you repay me?

338
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:07,279
Sister Dan, I...

339
00:21:07,280 --> 00:21:09,079
You're dropped.

340
00:21:45,676 --> 00:21:48,996
[He's trying to call Qinglang]

341
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,559
I'm crying.

342
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:57,880
I actually cried.

343
00:21:58,759 --> 00:22:00,598
Do you remember when
we were filming before,

344
00:22:00,599 --> 00:22:02,000
I could never cry?

345
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:07,440
Today, I cried.

346
00:22:09,599 --> 00:22:11,680
I found what Sister Lan talked about??

347
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:13,839
The fire in my heart.

348
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:18,960
Sister Lan always said the
fire in my heart had gone out,

349
00:22:19,599 --> 00:22:21,039
but now I've found it.

350
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:24,359
I found it!

351
00:22:28,039 --> 00:22:29,039
Qinglang.

352
00:22:30,240 --> 00:22:31,880
Are you happy for me?

353
00:22:41,790 --> 00:22:44,283
[Now he's calling his mom]

354
00:22:59,319 --> 00:23:00,319
Mom,

355
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:02,559
I can cry now.

356
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:06,000
Listen... You can't hear it?

357
00:23:06,599 --> 00:23:07,959
I'll make a...

358
00:23:07,960 --> 00:23:09,038
I'll record a video for you.

359
00:23:09,039 --> 00:23:10,159
I'll record a video for you.

360
00:24:11,526 --> 00:24:14,973
[Now he's posting his crash-out on
Weibo, with the caption "Mom, look!"]

361
00:24:20,046 --> 00:24:27,539
[His fans reacting, sharing
theories on his personal/work life]

362
00:24:55,759 --> 00:24:57,318
My luggage is still in the car.

363
00:24:57,319 --> 00:24:58,319
Get it tomorrow morning.

364
00:24:58,960 --> 00:24:59,960
Why tomorrow morning?

365
00:25:00,759 --> 00:25:02,519
I don't want to carry it. Do you?

366
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:05,440
I don't either.

367
00:26:36,759 --> 00:26:37,920
What do you want to watch?

368
00:26:39,440 --> 00:26:40,960
Your first on-screen kiss.

369
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:43,920
Turn it off.

370
00:26:49,759 --> 00:26:51,039
It's not like I haven't seen it.

371
00:26:51,519 --> 00:26:52,960
I'm not watching it with you.

372
00:26:56,319 --> 00:26:57,919
How about the one you won the award for?

373
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:01,160
Why do you keep watching my movies?

374
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:05,160
There's a secret.

375
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:17,920
A secret.

376
00:27:18,799 --> 00:27:19,839
A boy's secret.

377
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:24,599
Are we waking up early tomorrow?

378
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:26,440
No.

379
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:42,440
Ah.

380
00:27:42,599 --> 00:27:43,920
I need to charge.

381
00:27:46,799 --> 00:27:49,319
Does your charger cable fit my phone?

382
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:52,720
It's plugged in.

383
00:27:57,319 --> 00:27:59,199
My phone is going to
blow up once I turn it on.

384
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:17,160
How long have we been
disconnected from the world?

385
00:28:17,799 --> 00:28:18,960
72 hours.

386
00:28:21,160 --> 00:28:24,319
Can I keep it off and stay
disconnected for another 72 hours?

387
00:28:24,720 --> 00:28:25,720
No.

388
00:28:26,799 --> 00:28:27,799
Hmph.

389
00:28:29,559 --> 00:28:32,119
Feng Qinglang, you're an artist.

390
00:28:32,440 --> 00:28:34,720
Don't forget how many
contracts you're bound by.

391
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:37,839
It's a pity you're not an actor.

392
00:28:42,359 --> 00:28:44,319
The whole world is looking for me.

393
00:28:44,720 --> 00:28:46,559
Sister Lan, Sister Jialin...

394
00:28:46,799 --> 00:28:48,000
Even my mom.

395
00:28:49,559 --> 00:28:50,838
Call Qingtian first

396
00:28:50,839 --> 00:28:51,839
to see what's going on.

397
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:53,200
Okay.

398
00:28:56,839 --> 00:28:57,759
If you don't show up soon,

399
00:28:57,760 --> 00:28:59,240
everyone is going to call the police.

400
00:28:59,319 --> 00:29:00,775
"Xu Changyang, the human trafficker."

401
00:29:00,799 --> 00:29:01,920
Put Changyang on the phone.

402
00:29:07,039 --> 00:29:08,039
Xu Changyang.

403
00:29:08,599 --> 00:29:10,279
I can't believe I considered you a friend.

404
00:29:10,319 --> 00:29:12,359
When did you start coveting my brother?

405
00:29:13,599 --> 00:29:15,199
Was it before or after you turned legal?

406
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:20,119
Keep laughing.

407
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:21,560
You two will be crying soon enough.

408
00:29:22,119 --> 00:29:23,919
Reply to whoever is
looking for you yourself.

409
00:29:26,359 --> 00:29:28,573
[Unknown number calling]

410
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:40,319
I know it was my fault for not
telling you about the livestream linkup.

411
00:29:41,319 --> 00:29:43,000
But I just wanted to surprise you.

412
00:29:43,160 --> 00:29:44,160
What can I say?

413
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:46,160
Qinglang,

414
00:29:46,799 --> 00:29:48,559
Are you listening?

415
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:51,400
I used my alt account, Ji
Zongjun, to interact with you.

416
00:29:56,319 --> 00:29:57,319
He's gathering evidence.

417
00:29:59,519 --> 00:30:01,119
He's really good at acting sincere.

418
00:30:04,559 --> 00:30:07,559
So you were fooled by him back then?

419
00:30:09,920 --> 00:30:11,240
I wouldn't call it being fooled.

420
00:30:13,119 --> 00:30:14,920
Some moments were genuine.

421
00:30:21,799 --> 00:30:23,440
I need to call Sister Lan back.

422
00:30:44,559 --> 00:30:46,400
Feng Qinglang is finally back.

423
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,160
Sister Jialin.

424
00:30:48,599 --> 00:30:49,599
Where is Sister Lan?

425
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:51,519
She went to look for you.

426
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:53,720
Where did she go to look for me?

427
00:30:54,559 --> 00:30:57,095
President Xu gave Sister Lan
his brother's license plate number.

428
00:30:57,119 --> 00:30:58,799
Sister Lan had someone track the location.

429
00:30:58,960 --> 00:31:00,560
She has a general idea of where you are.

430
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:02,560
She and Brother Guo
are driving after you two.

431
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:06,600
I just tried calling Sister Lan,
but I couldn't get through.

432
00:31:06,720 --> 00:31:08,240
I'll try calling Brother Guo.

433
00:31:09,039 --> 00:31:10,160
I'll hang up now.

434
00:31:16,366 --> 00:31:22,512
[The "can't connect" message]

435
00:31:28,559 --> 00:31:29,559
There must be no signal.

436
00:31:35,359 --> 00:31:36,359
Sister Lan.

437
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,240
You're back in reach.

438
00:31:39,519 --> 00:31:42,079
Yes, I went off the grid.

439
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:43,519
As long as you're okay.

440
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:45,839
Where are you guys?

441
00:31:45,839 --> 00:31:46,839
Send me your location.

442
00:31:47,839 --> 00:31:48,480
Sister Lan.

443
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:49,480
Where are you now?

444
00:31:49,559 --> 00:31:50,680
This is Xu Changyang.

445
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:52,240
Hello.

446
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:53,720
Hello, Sister Lan.

447
00:31:53,759 --> 00:31:56,279
Don't worry, Qinglang is with me.

448
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:57,719
I'm familiar with the Molie area.

449
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:58,960
Are you still driving?

450
00:31:59,440 --> 00:32:01,319
Yes, we're navigating to Xi Gui now.

451
00:32:02,079 --> 00:32:02,880
It's not too far.

452
00:32:02,881 --> 00:32:04,079
But the road is rough.

453
00:32:04,319 --> 00:32:05,358
Don't drive tonight.

454
00:32:05,359 --> 00:32:06,656
Find a place to stay for the night.

455
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:08,815
We'll head out first thing tomorrow
morning to meet up with you.

456
00:32:08,839 --> 00:32:09,839
That works.

457
00:32:09,960 --> 00:32:13,078
Lang Di, how could you elope without me?

458
00:32:13,079 --> 00:32:13,839
And another thing,

459
00:32:13,840 --> 00:32:16,159
hurry up and send me a
photo of that human trafficker.

460
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:17,880
The shippers are going to lose their minds.

461
00:32:22,119 --> 00:32:24,440
Guo'er, find a place to stay nearby.

462
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:26,880
Sister,

463
00:32:27,079 --> 00:32:28,720
Shi Yuhao just posted a savage Weibo.

464
00:32:30,119 --> 00:32:35,494
[Yuhao just wailing away]

465
00:32:35,519 --> 00:32:36,559
Call Jialin.

466
00:32:37,079 --> 00:32:39,239
Tell him to release a statement
in the company's name,

467
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:41,640
announcing Qinglang's
withdrawal from the variety show.

468
00:32:49,359 --> 00:32:50,640
Sister Lan released a statement.

469
00:32:54,279 --> 00:32:56,999
Shi Yuhao's post is just to play
the victim and manipulate his fans.

470
00:32:58,079 --> 00:32:59,639
Lately, people have started digging into

471
00:32:59,640 --> 00:33:02,160
the financial backer behind Shi
Yuhao's variety show resources.

472
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:06,679
Some fans are linking Shi Yuhao's video

473
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:08,720
with Sister Lan's statement,

474
00:33:09,640 --> 00:33:11,079
saying Sister Lan is heartless

475
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:13,600
and is cutting off Shi Yuhao's livelihood.

476
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:17,640
Sister Lan shouldn't have
released the statement at this time.

477
00:33:17,920 --> 00:33:19,359
She's doing this to protect me.

478
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:21,119
She's drawing the fire to herself

479
00:33:22,559 --> 00:33:23,680
to control the situation.

480
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:29,160
Everyone thinks Sister Lan
was the one who took the show,

481
00:33:29,519 --> 00:33:31,359
and now she's the one pulling me out.

482
00:33:34,920 --> 00:33:37,279
I feel like we're back to how
things were seven years ago.

483
00:33:38,119 --> 00:33:39,119
Changyang...

484
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:49,038
Why are there so many people in this world

485
00:33:49,039 --> 00:33:51,519
who talk nonsense
without knowing the truth?

486
00:33:53,839 --> 00:33:56,519
Buddhism says reckless
speech creates bad karma,

487
00:33:56,839 --> 00:33:58,159
and bad karma brings retribution.

488
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:00,519
Aren't they afraid of retribution?

489
00:34:02,880 --> 00:34:04,279
They lack a sense of reverence.

490
00:34:13,079 --> 00:34:14,280
Hello, Sister Jialin.

491
00:34:14,760 --> 00:34:15,559
Guo,

492
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:16,760
where is Sister Lan?

493
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:18,079
She's driving.

494
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,440
Driving so late?

495
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:20,440
Why aren't you driving?

496
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,879
Oh, these winding mountain roads...

497
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:24,080
I don't dare to drive on them.

498
00:34:24,559 --> 00:34:25,559
What's going on?

499
00:34:26,159 --> 00:34:27,440
I found out a few things.

500
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:29,359
Jin Jin sent the recording
of her call with Shi Yuhao

501
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:31,639
to the variety show's investor.

502
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:34,479
If he wanted to bring Shi Yuhao down,

503
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:36,159
why didn't he send it directly to us?

504
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:38,159
He knew we wouldn't leak it.

505
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:39,719
It has no value to us.

506
00:34:40,519 --> 00:34:42,719
You shouldn't have
drawn the fire to yourself.

507
00:34:43,159 --> 00:34:44,558
Now that Shi Yuhao's dirt is out,

508
00:34:44,559 --> 00:34:47,119
we should release the video we have too.

509
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:49,936
The behind-the-scenes footage you
saved on the cloud drive back then,

510
00:34:49,960 --> 00:34:51,480
should be released if necessary.

511
00:34:52,639 --> 00:34:53,639
If we push him too hard,

512
00:34:53,640 --> 00:34:54,760
he might commit suicide.

513
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:57,440
When we were filming back then, he said

514
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,456
that because his friends
didn't understand him,

515
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:00,760
he almost committed suicide.

516
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:03,079
Poor kid.

517
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:05,840
Let him face his own karma.

518
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:12,679
Did your reshoots go smoothly today?

519
00:35:14,559 --> 00:35:15,880
Did I tell you to post that?

520
00:35:16,639 --> 00:35:18,999
Didn't you record the screen
because you wanted to post it?

521
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:21,440
But you didn't get my permission.

522
00:35:22,039 --> 00:35:23,439
I'm your manager.

523
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:25,680
Does the company need your
permission to make decisions?

524
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:27,639
Now is the perfect time.

525
00:35:27,679 --> 00:35:28,839
You called Qinglang,

526
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:29,880
and he didn't say a word.

527
00:35:30,039 --> 00:35:32,158
And Xing Lan took the blame
for pulling out of the show.

528
00:35:32,159 --> 00:35:34,079
Isn't this your chance to make a comeback?

529
00:35:35,920 --> 00:35:36,920
To put it bluntly,

530
00:35:37,039 --> 00:35:39,639
both you and Qinglang are
just puppets controlled by capital.

531
00:35:40,119 --> 00:35:42,638
Playing the victim is the
only way to gain more fans.

532
00:35:42,639 --> 00:35:44,079
Didn't I tell you

533
00:35:44,239 --> 00:35:45,518
that before you post anything,

534
00:35:45,519 --> 00:35:46,760
you must ask for my opinion?

535
00:35:47,079 --> 00:35:48,320
Are you out of your mind?

536
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:51,119
Haven't you caused enough
trouble for the company?

537
00:35:51,559 --> 00:35:54,279
The company is already being
merciful by not making you pay damages.

538
00:35:54,320 --> 00:35:56,079
Drop this victim mentality.

539
00:35:59,440 --> 00:36:01,416
The company has already booked
some commercial gigs for you.

540
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,960
Go home and rest for a couple of days,

541
00:36:03,079 --> 00:36:04,119
and get ready to work.

542
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:08,720
I want to terminate my contract.

543
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,880
Do you have 15 million?

544
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:22,679
Back then, the company
forced me to split the CP fans.

545
00:36:23,480 --> 00:36:24,638
If I hadn't split the fans so early,

546
00:36:24,639 --> 00:36:25,919
I wouldn't have offended Sister Lan,

547
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:26,880
and my career wouldn't have stalled,

548
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:27,880
leaving me like this.

549
00:36:28,079 --> 00:36:28,880
Shi Yuhao,

550
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:31,480
can you stop shifting the
blame to everyone else?

551
00:36:32,079 --> 00:36:33,518
You had both a girlfriend and a boyfriend.

552
00:36:33,519 --> 00:36:34,840
Why didn't you say so earlier?

553
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:37,215
Why didn't you tell us when
you couldn't hide it anymore?

554
00:36:37,239 --> 00:36:38,919
If the company hadn't
helped you split the fans early,

555
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:40,615
you would have crashed even
harder when the scandal broke.

556
00:36:40,639 --> 00:36:42,879
Did we make you offend Sister Lan?

557
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:44,078
When you were cursing and attacking people,

558
00:36:44,079 --> 00:36:45,639
why didn't you take a look at yourself?

559
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:47,359
When things go bad, you blame the company.

560
00:36:47,360 --> 00:36:49,256
But if things went well,
you'd run away even faster.

561
00:36:49,280 --> 00:36:50,320
On that point alone,

562
00:36:50,760 --> 00:36:52,640
you don't have a conscience
like Qinglang does.

563
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:55,880
He stayed by Sister Lan's side
through her toughest times.

564
00:36:56,159 --> 00:36:57,159
If it were you,

565
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:59,240
you would have run away long ago.

566
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:05,416
The company knows you
have no sense of responsibility.

567
00:37:05,440 --> 00:37:06,518
From now on, your affairs

568
00:37:06,519 --> 00:37:08,119
will still be decided by the company.

569
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:11,920
Go home and cry a few more
times these next few days,

570
00:37:12,239 --> 00:37:13,719
and post a couple more Weibo updates.

571
00:37:28,639 --> 00:37:30,405
[Erxi Culture + Media LTD]

572
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:32,840
You were absolutely right.

573
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,760
He was indeed recording for evidence.

574
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:37,400
Since he couldn't beat me,

575
00:37:37,519 --> 00:37:39,159
he targeted Sister Lan instead.

576
00:37:46,466 --> 00:37:48,639
Brother Guo, have you guys settled in?

577
00:37:52,468 --> 00:37:54,415
Not yet, Sister Lan is still driving.

578
00:37:56,280 --> 00:37:57,480
Let me know when you arrive.

579
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,880
Brother Guo asked for my photo earlier.

580
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:22,880
I'll record a video for him.

581
00:38:23,639 --> 00:38:24,639
What kind of video?

582
00:38:40,639 --> 00:38:41,639
Hello, Sister Lan.

583
00:38:44,039 --> 00:38:45,719
Aren't you recording this for Brother Guo?

584
00:38:58,880 --> 00:38:59,880
Hello, Sister Lan.

585
00:38:59,920 --> 00:39:01,079
My name is Xu Changyang.

586
00:39:01,519 --> 00:39:02,840
It's a pleasure to meet you.

587
00:39:03,360 --> 00:39:04,760
I've watched all of your films.

588
00:39:05,639 --> 00:39:07,639
Some critics say your films have regressed,

589
00:39:08,079 --> 00:39:10,159
shifting from exposure to consolation,

590
00:39:10,920 --> 00:39:11,920
losing their stance

591
00:39:12,079 --> 00:39:13,320
just to evoke empathy.

592
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:15,159
But I don't see it that way.

593
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:18,440
Of course, my opinion
might be insignificant,

594
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:20,880
but no matter the form of expression,

595
00:39:21,119 --> 00:39:22,880
it serves a purpose suited to its time.

596
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:25,079
A hundred years ago,

597
00:39:25,719 --> 00:39:27,599
Lu Xun used his writing
to expose human nature.

598
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:30,039
That exposure was like a sharp scalpel,

599
00:39:30,239 --> 00:39:31,999
cutting through the
rotting skin of the era.

600
00:39:35,079 --> 00:39:38,360
But today, most people live in anxiety.

601
00:39:39,119 --> 00:39:41,480
What this era needs more is
rebuilding after the exposure.

602
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,960
If we can only strip away the hypocrisy

603
00:39:44,320 --> 00:39:46,239
but cannot help the
decayed wood regenerate,

604
00:39:46,719 --> 00:39:49,119
the spirit of this world
will only perish faster.

605
00:39:51,079 --> 00:39:52,559
I've watched your films,

606
00:39:53,039 --> 00:39:54,840
and I can feel an enduring love in them,

607
00:39:55,039 --> 00:39:56,119
one that is indestructible.

608
00:39:56,960 --> 00:39:58,440
Although it's a kind of utopia,

609
00:39:59,079 --> 00:40:00,359
and it's not entirely realistic,

610
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:03,440
it's like a lighthouse. With it,

611
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:05,279
at least we have the hope and determination

612
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:06,719
to reach the other shore.

613
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:08,840
Without it,

614
00:40:09,280 --> 00:40:10,880
our lives would be even more of a waste.

615
00:40:13,639 --> 00:40:14,719
After saying all this,

616
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:16,960
what I really want to say is...

617
00:40:17,119 --> 00:40:19,519
your movies are the
reason I truly believe in love,

618
00:40:20,672 --> 00:40:24,512
and believe that I can find and protect it.

619
00:40:35,360 --> 00:40:37,415
How long did it take you to memorize that speech?

620
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:38,640
It just rolled off the tongue.

621
00:40:40,679 --> 00:40:41,679
Jealous?

622
00:40:42,239 --> 00:40:43,239
Send it to Sister Lan.

623
00:41:15,782 --> 00:41:18,328
[Message from Qinglang + Shi Haoyu calling]

624
00:41:18,639 --> 00:41:19,639
Sis,

625
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:21,880
It's Shi Yuhao, should I take it?

626
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:23,760
Yes.

627
00:41:36,148 --> 00:41:40,675
(Qingtian: Don't let my brother
hear, find somewhere and call me back)

628
00:41:43,440 --> 00:41:45,440
My delivery just arrived. I'll go grab it.

629
00:41:46,079 --> 00:41:47,440
When did you order food?

630
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:49,200
I was worried you'd get hungry.

631
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:55,079
Is this a good time to talk?

632
00:41:55,440 --> 00:41:56,960
Yes, I just stepped outside.

633
00:41:58,440 --> 00:42:00,256
Sister Lan and Brother
Guo were in a car accident.

634
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:01,880
Can you bring my brother here safely?

635
00:42:05,119 --> 00:42:06,119
I will.

636
00:44:18,950 --> 00:44:25,216
[A series of heartfelt messages to Sister Lan
asking to let him handle his matters on his own]

